articles.title: Georgia’s statewide races reflect shifting sentiments two years after Oct. 7 - AJC.com
articles.description: The ongoing war in Gaza is a hot topic for candidates for U.S. Senate and governor, as local Jews and Arab Americans gather to commemorate the Oct. 7, 2023, attacks on Israel.
